## ✅ `.gitignore` — Adaptado a React, PHP y WordPress

```gitignore
# Node.js
node_modules/
dist/
.vite/
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# IDEs
.vscode/
.idea/

# macOS
.DS_Store

# PHP / Composer
vendor/
composer.lock

# WordPress
wp-config.php
wp-content/uploads/
wp-content/cache/
wp-content/upgrade/
wp-content/advanced-cache.php
wp-content/wp-cache-config.php
wp-content/debug.log

# Otros archivos sensibles
*.log
*.zip
*.bak
*.sql
*.sqlite

# React build (opcional si se genera)
react-frontend/build/
